== 反响 ==
=== 評價 ===
根據[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]的146條評論，擁有98%超高鮮度，平均得分7.9／10，觀眾分數平均為88%<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/paddington_2014 |title=Paddington (2015) |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |accessdate=2018-06-10 |archive-date=2019-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403052025/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/paddington_2014/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影獲得了77分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/paddington|title=Paddington|publisher=[[CBS|CBS]]|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2018-06-10|archive-date=2020-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200823074456/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/paddington|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
英国方面，首周末取得800万美元，这成为 StudioCanal 公司作品最高首映成绩以及年度第二高(第一是动画片《[[乐高大电影|乐高大电影]]》)的家庭电影首映成绩<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2014/dec/02/paddington-beats-hunger-games-mockingjay-part-1-at-uk-box-office|title=All aboard the Paddington express to UK box office supremacy|author=Charles Gant|work=the Guardian|accessdate=18 January 2015|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322040100/https://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2014/dec/02/paddington-beats-hunger-games-mockingjay-part-1-at-uk-box-office|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Paddington gets bear hug from UK cinema audiences|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-30296130|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate=3 December 2014|date=2 December 2014|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129085811/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-30296130|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://deadline.com/2014/12/paddington-gives-studio-canal-its-biggest-ever-uk-opening-1201304063/ | title = ‘Paddington’ Gives Studio Canal Its Biggest Ever UK Opening | author = Ali Jaafar | publisher = Deadline.com | date = 1 December 2014 | accessdate = 3 January 2015 | archive-date = 2021-02-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210213075210/https://deadline.com/2014/12/paddington-gives-studio-canal-its-biggest-ever-uk-opening-1201304063/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

北美方面，于2015年1月16日上映<ref name="Inside Release">{{cite web|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/10/15/paddington-and-hot-tub-time-machine-2-pushed-to-early-2015/|title='Paddington' and 'Hot Tub Time Machine 2' pushed to early 2015|work=EW.com|accessdate=19 November 2014|archive-date=2015-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150111093401/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/10/15/paddington-and-hot-tub-time-machine-2-pushed-to-early-2015/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，首周末获得1920万美元，次于战争片《[[美国狙击手|美国狙击手]]》和喜剧片 ''The Wedding Ringer'' 列第三位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2015&wknd=03&p=.htm|title=Weekend Box Office Results for January 16-18, 2015 - Box Office Mojo|work=boxofficemojo.com|accessdate=19 January 2015|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610152610/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2015&wknd=03&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

中国大陆方面，首周四天获得4800万人民币列第六位，次周收3500万蝉联第六位，第三周收1250万列第八位，最终累计1.012亿。

